{
    "name": "Octopus",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Ecology",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Environment</b> temperate or cold ocean<br/><b>Organization</b> solitary<br/><b>Treasure</b> none"
        },
        {
            "name": "Special Abilities",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "<b>Ink Cloud (Ex)</b> An octopus can emit a 10-foot-radius sphere of ink once per minute as a free action. The ink provides total concealment in water, and persists for 1 minute.<br/><br/><b>Jet (Ex)</b> An octopus can jet backward once per round as a full-round action, at a speed of 200 feet. It must move in a straight line while jetting, and does not provoke attacks of opportunity when it does so.<br/><br/><b>Poison (Ex)</b> Bite\u2014injury; <i>save </i>Fort DC 13; <i>frequency </i>1/round for 6 rounds; <i>effect </i>1 Str; <i>cure </i>1 save."
        },
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "The octopus is a cunning animal capable of using complex tactics to get food."
        }
    ],
    "html": "<i>Eight tentacles, each adorned with rows of countless suckers, unfurl from the barrel-shaped body of this large-eyed creature.</i>",
